NK029(ha)003:1: // dang po phyi dbang gi chu bo las /
NK029(ha)003:2: yo ga'i dbang gi them skas bzhugs so //
NK029(ha)003:3: drug pa yo ga'i dbang la gnyis ste /
NK029(ha)003:4: dkyil 'khor las kyi rim pa dang /
NK029(ha)003:7: tshad dang ldan pa'i sa stegs la //
NK029(ha)003:8: dri bzang chu yis chag chag gdab //
NK029(ha)003:9: byin rlabs ldan pa'i thig skud kyis //
NK029(ha)003:10: cha chen bcu drug legs par gdab //
NK029(ha)003:11: de nas cha bran gdab pa ni //
NK029(ha)003:12: dang po phyed gdab phyi ma gdab //
NK029(ha)003:13: gnyis pa cha bzhi mnyam du gdab //
NK029(ha)003:14: gsum pa phyi'i cha gcig gdab //
NK029(ha)003:15: bzhi pa lha snam phyed du gdab //
NK029(ha)003:16: lnga pa dbus dor mtha' gnyis gdab //
NK029(ha)003:17: drug pa phyed gdab phyi ma gdab //
NK029(ha)003:18: bdun pa cha bzhi mnyam du gdab //
NK029(ha)003:19: brgyad pa dbus dor mtha' gnyis gdab //
NK029(ha)003:20: de nas mu khyud bskor ba ni //
NK029(ha)003:21: cha chen gsum nas pho brang bskor //
NK029(ha)003:22: nang du cha bran nyer bzhi yod //
NK029(ha)003:23: brgyad kyi dbus kyi ling tshe yin //
NK029(ha)003:24: drug drug phyogs bzhi'i ling tshe la //
NK029(ha)003:26: dbus dang phyogs bzhi ling tshe la //
NK029(ha)003:27: pad+ma 'dab ma bzhi pa'am //'khor lo rtsibs bzhi re res bskor //
NK029(ha)003:28: glang gur rdo ra spyi dang mtshungs //
NK029(ha)003:29: mda' yab zur thig phrad so nas //
NK029(ha)003:30: pad 'dab rdo ra me ri la //
NK029(ha)003:31: ci rigs mtshams pas bskor bar bya //
NK029(ha)003:32: byin brlabs ldan pa'i tshon rtsi yis //
NK029(ha)003:33: mkhas pas re kha legs par bri //
NK029(ha)003:35: dbus kyi lte ba dkar po bya //
NK029(ha)003:36: phyogs bzhi sngo ser dmar dang ljang //'dab ma bzhi ni phyogs kyi mdog /
NK029(ha)003:37: mu khyud gdung bzhi nag po byed //
NK029(ha)003:38: mtshams kyi ling tshe mdzes tshon la //
NK029(ha)003:39: gru chad bzhi ni phyogs las log /
NK029(ha)003:40: lha snam shar sngo lho phyogs ser /
NK029(ha)003:41: nub dmar byang ni ljang khu byed //
NK029(ha)003:42: rtsigs pa la sogs gong dang mthun //
NK029(ha)003:43: de nas rnam pa dgod pa ni //
NK029(ha)003:44: dbus su rnam snang yum bzhi dgod //
NK029(ha)003:45: shar du mi skyod sems dpa' bzhi //
NK029(ha)003:46: lho ru rin 'byung sems dpa' bzhi //
NK029(ha)003:47: nub du mtha' yas sems dpa' bzhi //
NK029(ha)003:48: byang du don grub sems dpa' bzhi //
NK029(ha)003:49: mtshams kyi ling tshe bzhi pa la //
NK029(ha)003:50: sgeg mo bzhi'i tsag li dgod //
NK029(ha)003:51: gru chad bzhi la gdugs sogs bzhi //
NK029(ha)003:52: blo 'bur bzhi la sgo ba bzhi //
NK029(ha)003:53: lha snam skal bzang sems dpa' stong //
NK029(ha)003:54: gsung thugs rten ni gong dang mtshungs //
NK029(ha)003:55: lhag chad gsal zhing zhal gsos mchod //
NK029(ha)003:56: mchod yon la sogs phyi mchod dang //
NK029(ha)003:57: gtor ma bshams pa la sogs dang //
NK029(ha)003:58: bum sogs bsham pa gong dang mthun //
NK029(ha)003:59: de ni bar skabs kyi tshigs su bcad pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:60: de nas rab gnas kyi dod ni /
NK029(ha)003:61: dpon slob rnams gdan la bzhugs shing /
NK029(ha)003:62: sngon 'gro gtor ma cha bzhi'i cha gcig bsham la /
NK029(ha)003:63: byin gyis rlabs la bsngo zhing /
NK029(ha)003:65: mchod pa byin gyis rlabs pa dang /
NK029(ha)003:66: skyabs 'gro sems bskyed bsrung 'khor bsgom pa rnams gong du song nas /
NK029(ha)003:69: stong pa'i ngang las h+aum yam /
NK029(ha)003:70: h+aum las rdo rje'i mtshan pa'i rlung gi dkyil 'khor /
NK029(ha)003:71: de'i steng du h+aum bam h+aum las 'o ma'i tsho
NK029(ha)003:72: de'i steng du h+aum lam h+aum las gser gyi sa
NK029(ha)003:73: gzhi de'i steng du h+aum bam h+aum las rgya mtsho
NK029(ha)003:74: chen po bsam / de'i steng du h+aum sum las
NK029(ha)003:75: ri'i rgyal po ri rab zur bzhi pa rin po
NK029(ha)003:76: che sna bzhi'i rang bzhin can /
NK029(ha)003:77: rin po che sna tshogs kyis brgyan pa /
NK029(ha)003:78: 'og gzhi de rnams sna tshogs rdo rje'i rang bzhin du byin gyis rlabs /
NK029(ha)003:80: b+h+rum las rin po che sna tshogs las grub pa'i gzhal yas khang gru bzhi /
NK029(ha)003:82: rta babs dang bcas pa'i rdo rje dang /
NK029(ha)003:83: nor bu rin po che las byas pa /
NK029(ha)003:84: dbus rnam snang gi gnas su ahsim ahls seng ge'i khri /
NK029(ha)003:86: h+aum las glang po che'i khri /
NK029(ha)003:89: nub du hrihmam hrihls rma bya'i khri /
NK029(ha)003:90: byang du ahgamahahlasa nam mkha' lding gi khri /
NK029(ha)003:91: lha gzhan thams cad kyi gnas su hrih las pad+ma dang /
NK029(ha)003:92: gtso bo lnga'i pad+ma'i steng du /
NK029(ha)003:94: dbus kyi seng ge pad zla'i steng du /
NK029(ha)003:95: rnam snang dkar po rdo rje dkyil dkrungs gis bzhugs pa /
NK029(ha)003:96: phyag gnyis byang chub mchog gi phyag rgyas de bzhin
NK029(ha)003:97: gshegs pa'i rdo rje rtse lnga pa bsnams pa zhal
NK029(ha)003:98: bzhi pa zhal dang po shar du gzigs pa /
NK029(ha)003:99: rnam snang gi mdun gyi pad 'dab la /
NK029(ha)003:100: sems ma rdo rje ma'i ngo bo rdo rje rtse lnga pa dmar po /
NK029(ha)003:101: g.yas su rin po che rdo rje ma'i ngo bo yid bzhin nor bu rin po che /
NK029(ha)003:102: rtse mo rdo rje lnga pas mtshan pa /
NK029(ha)003:103: rgyab du rdo rje chos ma'i ngo bo pad ma dkar dmar 'dab ma bcu drug pa la /
NK029(ha)003:104: 'dab ma brgyad mthur du gyes shing kha bye ba /
NK029(ha)003:105: 'dab ma brgyad steng du bltas pas /
NK029(ha)003:106: kha ma bye ba'i nang na /
NK029(ha)003:107: dang po'i rdo rje rtse lnga pa chud pa /
NK029(ha)003:108: g.yon du rdo rje las ma'i ngo bo sna tshogs steng rdo rje bcu gnyis pa lte ba dkar /
NK029(ha)003:110: g.yas kyi ser g.yon gyi ljang /
NK029(ha)003:112: shar gyi dbus su glang po che'i khri dang /
NK029(ha)003:113: pad zla la mi skyod pa sngon po sa gnon
NK029(ha)003:114: gyi phyag rgyas de ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i rdo
NK029(ha)003:115: rje rtse lnga pa bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)003:116: mdun gyi pad 'dab la rdo rje sems dpa' dkar po /
NK029(ha)003:117: phyag g.yas pa'i sor mo gsum sbreng ba'i rtse mo
NK029(ha)003:118: la dang po'i rdo rje rtse lnga pa rang gi
NK029(ha)003:119: thugs khar stod pa'i tshul gyis 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)003:120: g.yon na rdo rje khu tshur gyi dril bu kha nang du bstan pa /
NK029(ha)003:121: snyan pa'i tshul gyis skur brten pa /
NK029(ha)003:122: g.yas su rdo rje rgyal po gser mdog phyag gnyis
NK029(ha)003:123: rdo rje lcags kyus de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK029(ha)003:125: g.yon du chags pa dmar po rdo rjes mtshan pa'i
NK029(ha)003:126: mdas ut+pa la dmar po kha bye ba'i made'u can
NK029(ha)003:127: / rdo rje gzhu rna ba'i bar du bkang nas /
NK029(ha)003:128: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams la 'bigs par mdzad pa /
NK029(ha)003:129: rgyab tu legs par ljang khu dang po'i rdo rje
NK029(ha)003:130: rtse lnga pa gnyis bsnams nas legs so sbyin pa'i
NK029(ha)003:131: tshul gyis de bzhin gshegs pa rnams mnyes par mdzad
NK029(ha)003:132: pa / lhor rta'i khri la pad zla la rin 'byung ser po /
NK029(ha)003:133: mchog sbyin gyi phyag rgya rdo rje rin po che
NK029(ha)003:134: bsnams pa mdun gyi pad 'dab la rin po che
NK029(ha)003:135: ser pos phyag g.yas rin po che rang gi dbang
NK029(ha)003:137: g.yon rdo rje khu tshur gyis dril bu kha nang
NK029(ha)003:138: du bstan nas snyem pa'i tshul gyis skur rten pa
NK029(ha)003:139: / g.yas su nyi ma nyi ma'i mdog can phyag
NK029(ha)003:140: g.yas kyi nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi lte ba na
NK029(ha)003:141: / / rdo rje rtse lnga pa yod pa'i 'od
NK029(ha)003:142: kyis de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad snang bar mdzad
NK029(ha)003:143: pa thugs khar 'dzin cing g.yon pa gdan la rten
NK029(ha)003:144: / / pa'o // g.yon du rdo rje rgyal mtshan
NK029(ha)003:145: sngon po phyag g.yas pa'i dang po rdo rjes mtshan
NK029(ha)003:146: pa'i yid bzhin nor bu'i tog can gyi rgyal mtshan
NK029(ha)003:147: dar dang mu tig gi chun 'phyang la sogs pa'i
NK029(ha)003:148: brgyan gyis spras pa phrag pa'i phyogs su sbreng ba'i
NK029(ha)003:149: tshul gyis 'dzin pa de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK029(ha)003:150: sbyin pa'i pha rol du phyin pa la nges par
NK029(ha)003:151: sbyor bar mdzad pa g.yon pa gdan la rten pa'o
NK029(ha)003:152: / / pa'o // // g.yon du gzhad pa dung dang pad+ma'i rtsa ba ltar dkar ba /
NK029(ha)003:153: g.yas kyi dang po'i rdo rje rtse lnga pa gnyis
NK029(ha)003:154: kyi dbus su chud pa'i so'i 'phreng ba gnyis kha
NK029(ha)003:155: 'gram g.yas su 'dzin pas de pa thams cad 'dzun
NK029(ha)003:156: pa smad du byung ba la /
NK029(ha)003:157: nges par sbyor ba g.yon pa gdan la rten pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:158: nub du rma bya'i khri dang pad zla la 'od
NK029(ha)003:159: dpag med dmar po mnyam bzhag gi phyag rgyas rdo
NK029(ha)003:160: rje pad+ma la chos dkar dmar phyag g.yon snyem pa
NK029(ha)003:161: dang bcas pas rdo rje pad+ma'i gdong bu skur rten
NK029(ha)003:162: cing g.yas pa'i rdo rje khu tshur gyis theb 'dzug
NK029(ha)003:163: gyis snying khar rdo rje pad+ma'i 'dab ma kha 'byed
NK029(ha)003:164: pa'o // g.yas su rnon po sngon po phyag g.yon
NK029(ha)003:165: pa'i rdo rje khu tshur gyis thugs kar shes rab
NK029(ha)003:166: kyi pha rol du phyin pa'i po ti bsnams shing
NK029(ha)003:167: pa'o // / g.yas pa rdo rje ral gri de
NK029(ha)003:168: bzhin gshegs pa thams cad la 'debs pa'i tshul du
NK029(ha)003:170: rgyu gser gyi mdog can phyag g.yas pa'i gung mo'i rtse mo na /
NK029(ha)003:171: dang po'i rdo rje rtse gcig pa'i dbyibs can gyis
NK029(ha)003:172: 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad pa bskor ba'i tshul du 'dzin
NK029(ha)003:173: zhing g.yon pa gdan la rten pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:174: rgyab du smra ba zangs gyi mdog can phyag g.yas
NK029(ha)003:175: pa dang po'i rdo rjes mtshan pa'i lce bsnam nas
NK029(ha)003:176: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad la smra bar mdzad
NK029(ha)003:177: cing / g.yon pa gdan la brten pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:179: mkha' lding gi khri dang pad zla la don 'grub
NK029(ha)003:180: ljang khu skyabs sbyin gyis phyag rgyas sna tshogs rdo
NK029(ha)003:181: rje bsnams pa / mdun gyi pad 'dab la /
NK029(ha)003:182: las zhal dang byin pa gnyis nas zhabs kyi bar dkar po /
NK029(ha)003:183: zhal gyi 'og nas skyed pa'i bar dmar skya /
NK029(ha)003:184: skyed pa'i bar dang phyag gnyis sngo skya /
NK029(ha)003:187: phyag g.yas pa sna tshogs rdo rje rtse bcu gnyis pa thugs khar gtod pa'i tshul gyis 'dzin cing /
NK029(ha)003:188: g.yon snyems pa dang bcas pas sna tshogs rdo rjes
NK029(ha)003:189: yu ba byas pa'i dril bu kha nang du bstan
NK029(ha)003:190: bskur rten pa'o // g.yas su bsrung ba gser gyi
NK029(ha)003:191: mdog can phyag gnyis kyi mtha' gnyis su rdo rje
NK029(ha)003:192: rtse lnga pas mtshan pa'i rdo rje go cha bsnams
NK029(ha)003:193: nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad la go dkon
NK029(ha)003:195: g.yon du gnod sbyin nag po lto ba yangs pa
NK029(ha)003:196: zhal mche ba gtsigs pa khro bo rdo rje rtse
NK029(ha)003:197: lnga pas lte bar mtshan pa'i mche ba zhal gyi
NK029(ha)003:198: grwa gnyis su 'dzin pa de bzhin gshegs pa thams
NK029(ha)003:199: cad la sdig pa'i tshul du mdzad pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:200: rgyab du khu tshur ser po dam tshig gi rdo
NK029(ha)003:201: rje khu tshur gyis dang po'i rdo rje rtse lnga
NK029(ha)003:202: pa'i 'tshir ba'i tshul gyis bzhugs pa /
NK029(ha)003:203: shar lho'i ling tsher sgeg mo ma dkar mo phyag
NK029(ha)003:204: gnyis kyis rdo rje rtse lnga pa gnyis skems pa'i
NK029(ha)003:205: tshul gyis 'dzin cing g.yon du cung zad 'dud pa'o
NK029(ha)003:206: // lho nub kyi ling tsher 'phreng ba ser mo
NK029(ha)003:207: rdo rje rin po che'i 'phreng ba'i de bzhin gshegs
NK029(ha)003:208: pa thams cad la dbang bskur bar mdzad pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:209: nub byang gi ling tsher glu ma dkar dmar phyag
NK029(ha)003:210: gnyis rdo rjes mtshan pa'i pi wang brdung ba la
NK029(ha)003:211: brtson pa'o // byang shar gyi ling tsher /
NK029(ha)003:212: gar ma sna tshogs mdog phyag gnyis rdo rje rtse gsum pa gnyis bsnams nas gar stabs byed pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:214: bdug pa ma dkar mo phyag gnyis rdo rje rtse
NK029(ha)003:215: lnga pas mtshan pa'i spos snams pas de bzhin gshegs
NK029(ha)003:216: pa thams cad tshim par mdzad pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:217: lho nub kyi grar me tog ma ser mo phyag
NK029(ha)003:218: g.yon rdo rje me tog gi snod 'dzin cing g.yas
NK029(ha)003:219: me tog gis char 'bebs par mdzad pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:220: nub byang gi grar mar me ma dkar dmar phyag
NK029(ha)003:221: gnyis rdo rje mar me'i sdong bu bsnams te de
NK029(ha)003:222: bzhin gshegs pa rnams snang ba'i tshogs kyis tshim par
NK029(ha)003:223: mdzad pa'o // byang shar gyi grar /
NK029(ha)003:224: byug pa ma sna tshogs mdog phyag g.yon rdo rjes
NK029(ha)003:225: mtshan pa'i dri'i dung phor bsnams ste phyag g.yas kyi
NK029(ha)003:226: dri'i sprin gyis de bzhin gshegs pa rnams mchod par
NK029(ha)003:227: mdzad pa'o // shar gyi blo 'bur la /
NK029(ha)003:228: lcags kyu dkar po phyag gnyis kyis rdo rje'i mtshan
NK029(ha)003:229: pa'i lcags kyu bsnams nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams
NK029(ha)003:231: lhor zhags pa ser po phyag gnyis rdo rje zhags
NK029(ha)003:232: pas de bzhin gshegs pa rnams 'jug par mdzad pa'o
NK029(ha)003:233: // nub la lcags sgrogs dkar dmar phyag gnyis rdo
NK029(ha)003:234: rje lcags sgrogs de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad 'ching
NK029(ha)003:235: // bar mdzad pa'o // byang rdo rje 'bebs pa
NK029(ha)003:236: sna tshogs mdog phyag g.yas rdo rje dril bu bsnams
NK029(ha)003:237: nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad 'bebs par mdzad
NK029(ha)003:238: pa g.yon gdan la rten pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:239: gong gi rigs sngar lnga po la /
NK029(ha)003:240: nyi ma'i 'od kyi rgyab yol mnga' ba /
NK029(ha)003:241: lha rdzas kyi dar la'i stod g.yogs smad g.yogs mnabs pa /
NK029(ha)003:242: rin po che'i cod pan dang dar dpyangs kyi dbang bskur ba dang ldan pa /
NK029(ha)003:243: rdo rje sems dpa' man chad rab dgyes pas /
NK029(ha)003:244: spyan gdangs pa sgeg pa'i nyams can 'dzum bag dang bcas pa /
NK029(ha)003:245: sangs rgyas lnga'i cod pan dang dar dpyangs kyi dbang bskur mdang ldan pa /
NK029(ha)003:246: rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa /
NK029(ha)003:247: dar dkar pa'i stod g.yogs dang smad g.yogs bcas pa /
NK029(ha)003:248: pad zla'i gdan la sems dpa'i dkyil mo dkrungs gis bzhugs pa /
NK029(ha)003:249: zla ba'i rgyab yol can no //
NK029(ha)003:250: de nas lha rnams la bskal bzang stong du bzhis ma tshang ba /
NK029(ha)003:251: phyogs rer nyis brgya bzhi bcu rtsa dgu dgu sems
NK029(ha)003:252: dpa' dang po bzhi dang 'dra pa la khyad par
NK029(ha)003:253: rdo rje rin po che cod pan gyi dbang bskur
NK029(ha)003:259: mun pa nges par 'joms pa'i blo gros /
NK029(ha)003:266: bzang skyong grwa ba can gyi 'od /
NK029(ha)003:267: byang du rdo rje snying po /
NK029(ha)003:270: kun tu bzang po rnams sems dpa' dang po bzhi dang 'dra ba la /
NK029(ha)003:271: khyad par rdo rje rin po che cod pan gyi dbang bskur ba'o //
NK029(ha)003:272: sgo bzhir sgo ma bzhi gong bzhin sgom /
NK029(ha)003:273: lha tshogs de rnams kyi spyi bor +amo /
NK029(ha)003:276: rang bzhin gnas nas ye shes pa snyan gsan dbab cing spyan drangs /
NK029(ha)003:277: de nas spyan drangs pa ni /
NK029(ha)003:279: ma lus sems can kun gyi dbang gyur ba /
NK029(ha)003:280: bdud sde dpung bcas ma lus 'joms mdzad pa /
NK029(ha)003:281: dngos rnams ma lus ji bzhin mkhyen gyur pa'i /
NK029(ha)003:282: bcom ldan rnam snang 'khor bcas gshegs su gsol /
NK029(ha)003:283: e h+ya hi b+ha ga wan ma h+aa ka ru ni ka tri sha ho sa ma ya stam /
NK029(ha)003:284: bcom ldan 'di ni byon pa legs /
NK029(ha)003:285: bdag ni bsod nams skal par ldan /
NK029(ha)003:286: bdag gi mchod yon bzhes nas kyang /
NK029(ha)003:287: thugs rjes thugs dbag mdzad du gsol /
NK029(ha)003:289: badz+ra ga ga na kham sa ma ye s+w+aah+aa /
NK029(ha)003:290: ji ltar ltams pa tsam gyis kyang /
NK029(ha)003:291: lha rnams kyis ni khrus gsol ba /
NK029(ha)003:292: lha'i chu ni dag pa yi /
NK029(ha)003:293: de bzhin bdag gis sku khrus gsol //
NK029(ha)003:294: mo badz+ra sarba de ba sa ta ya tsa ha ti ya mi te ta ra s+w+aa h+aa /
NK029(ha)003:295: bdag dang 'gro la thugs rtse'i phyir /
NK029(ha)003:296: nyid kyi rdzu 'phrul mthu yis ni /
NK029(ha)003:297: ji srid mchod pa bdag 'bul na /
NK029(ha)003:298: ji srid bcom ldan bzhugs su gsol /
NK029(ha)003:299: pad+ma ka ma la ye h+aum /
NK029(ha)003:300: me tog dam pa 'di dag dang /
NK029(ha)003:301: de bzhin chu skyes thang skyes dang /
NK029(ha)003:302: mchog du dad pas bdag 'bul na /
NK029(ha)003:303: ci bde bar ni bzhes su gsol /
NK029(ha)003:304: +amo na ma sarba ta tha ga ta pus pa
NK029(ha)003:305: pu tsa me ga sa mun tra pa ra na
NK029(ha)003:307: lhan cig skyes dang sbyar bas mchog /
NK029(ha)003:308: bdug spos dam pa 'di dag ni /
NK029(ha)003:309: mchog du dad pas bdag 'bul na /
NK029(ha)003:310: ci bde bar ni bzhes su gsol /
NK029(ha)003:312: mun pa'i tshogs rnams 'dzoms mdzad pa /
NK029(ha)003:313: phyogs kun gsal byed mar me 'di //
NK029(ha)003:314: kun mkhyen dngos grub thob bya'i phyir //
NK029(ha)003:315: mchog du dad pas bdag 'bul na //
NK029(ha)003:316: ci bde bar ni bzhes su gsol //
NK029(ha)003:318: yang dag par ni sbyar ba'i mchog /
NK029(ha)003:319: dri mchog dam pa 'di dag ni //
NK029(ha)003:320: mchog du dad pas bdag 'bul na //

NK029(ha)003:720: nges pa'i rgyal po rdo rje mchog /
NK029(ha)003:721: rdo rje rgyal pos dbang bskur ro //

NK029(ha)003:723: rdo rje chags pa bde chen po //
NK029(ha)003:724: rdo rje 'da' ni dbang byed pa //
NK029(ha)003:725: bdud kyi 'dod pa rdo rje che //
NK029(ha)003:726: rdo rje chags pa'i dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)003:729: rdo rje legs pa sems dpa' mchog /
NK029(ha)003:730: rdo rje mgu ba dga' ba che //

NK029(ha)003:732: rdo rje legs pa'i dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)003:735: rin chen rdo rje 'bar ba'i me //
NK029(ha)003:736: mnyam nyid ye shes rdo rje sku //
NK029(ha)003:737: rdo rje mchog sbyin phyag rgya mdzad //
NK029(ha)003:738: rin chen 'byung gnas dbang bskur ro //

NK029(ha)003:740: rdo rje rin chen rdo rje don //
NK029(ha)003:741: rdo rje nam mkha' nor bu che //
NK029(ha)003:742: nam mkha' snying po rdo rje phyug /
NK029(ha)003:743: rdo rje rin chen dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)003:746: rdo rje gzi brjid cher 'bar ba //
NK029(ha)003:747: rdo rje nyi ma rgyal ba'i 'od //
NK029(ha)003:748: rdo rje 'od zer gzi brjid che //
NK029(ha)003:749: rdo rje gzi brjid dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)003:752: sems can don rab mdzad don dpal //
NK029(ha)003:753: rdo rje rgyal mtshan rab dga' phyed //
NK029(ha)003:754: rdo rje chen po rin chen dpal //
NK029(ha)003:755: rdo rje rgyal mtshan dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)003:756: badz+ra ke du a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK029(ha)003:757: rdo rje bzhad mo bzhad pa che //
NK029(ha)003:758: rdo rje 'dzum pa ngo mtshar che //
NK029(ha)003:759: dga' zhing rab dga' rdo rje'i don //
NK029(ha)003:760: rdo rje dga' ba'i dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)003:763: mtha' yas rdo rje chos kyi sku //
NK029(ha)003:764: kun rtogs ye shes rdo rje'i sku //
NK029(ha)003:765: rdo rje ting nge 'dzin phyag rgya mdzad //
NK029(ha)003:766: snang ba mtha' yas dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)003:767: badz+ra d+harma a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum //
NK029(ha)003:768: rdo rje chos rab rdo rje don //
NK029(ha)003:769: rdo rje pad+ma rab dga' byed //'jig rten dbang phyug chos rab spyan //
NK029(ha)003:770: rdo rje chos kyi dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)003:771: badz+ra d+harma a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum //
NK029(ha)003:772: rdo rje gnon po theg pa che //
NK029(ha)003:773: rdo rje ral gri mtshon chen po //'jam dpal rdo rje rab tu dga' //
NK029(ha)003:774: rdo rje gnon pa'i dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)003:775: badz+ra tik+sh+na a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum //
NK029(ha)003:776: rdo rje rgyu dang snying po che //
NK029(ha)003:777: rdo rje 'khor lo tshul chen po //
NK029(ha)003:778: rab bskor rdo rje las byung ba //
NK029(ha)003:779: rdo rje rgyu yis dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)003:782: rdo rje gsung ba rang rig mchog /
NK029(ha)003:783: rdo rje bzlas pa rab sgrub sbyin //
NK029(ha)003:784: mi gsung rdo rje mchog sgrub pa //
NK029(ha)003:785: rdo rje gsung gi dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)003:786: rdo rje badz+ra b+ha sha a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK029(ha)003:787: don 'grub rdo rje skyod mdzad glu //
NK029(ha)003:788: grub pa ye shes rdo rje'i sku //
NK029(ha)003:789: rdo rje skyabs sbyin phyag rgya mdzad //
NK029(ha)003:790: don 'grub rdo rje'i dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)003:791: badz+ra karma a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK029(ha)003:792: rdo rje las rab rdo rje'i bka' //
NK029(ha)003:793: las kyi rdo rje kun rab sgrol //
NK029(ha)003:794: rdo rje nges pa rgya che ba //
NK029(ha)003:795: rdo rje las rab dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)003:796: badz+ra karma a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK029(ha)003:797: rdo rje bsrung ba bstan pa che //
NK029(ha)003:798: rdo rje brtson 'grus dka' thub pa //
NK029(ha)003:799: rdo rje brtson 'grus mchog thub pa //
NK029(ha)003:800: rdo rje bsrung ba'i dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)003:801: badz+ra rak+sha a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK029(ha)003:802: rdo rje gnod sbyin thabs chen po //
NK029(ha)003:803: rdo rje mche ba gtsigs pa che //
NK029(ha)003:804: bdud 'joms rdo rje mi zad pa //
NK029(ha)003:805: rdo rje gnod sbyin dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)003:806: badz+ra yak+sha a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK029(ha)003:807: rdo rje mtshams sbyor rab tu 'dud //
NK029(ha)003:808: rdo rje bcings pa rab grol byed //
NK029(ha)003:809: rdo rje khu tshur dam tshig mchog /
NK029(ha)003:810: rdo rje khu tshur dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)003:811: badz+ra mush+ti a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK029(ha)003:812: shar phyogs lha mo la se ma //
NK029(ha)003:814: phyag gnyis phyag rgya khu tshur 'chang //
NK029(ha)003:815: la se ma yi dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)003:816: badz+ra la se a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK029(ha)003:817: lho phyogs lha mo ma le ma //
NK029(ha)003:819: phyag mtshan phyag gnyis 'phreng ba bsnams //
NK029(ha)003:820: ma le ma yi dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)003:821: badz+ra ma le a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum //
NK029(ha)003:822: nub phyogs lha mo girti ma //
NK029(ha)003:824: phyag mtshan phyag gnyis pi wang bsnams /
NK029(ha)003:825: girti ma yi dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)003:828: byang phyogs lha mo nirti ma /
NK029(ha)003:830: phyag mtshan phyag gnyis gar bsgyur ma //
NK029(ha)003:831: nirti ma yi dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)003:832: badz+ra nirti a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum //
NK029(ha)003:833: shar lho lha mo d+hu pe ma //
NK029(ha)003:835: phyag mtshan phyag na spos khang bsnams //
NK029(ha)003:836: d+hu pe ma yi dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)003:839: lho nub lha mo push+pe ma //
NK029(ha)003:841: phyag mtshan phyag na me tog bsnams //
NK029(ha)003:842: push+pe ma yi dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)003:843: badz+ra push+pe a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK029(ha)003:844: nub byang lha mo a lo ke //
NK029(ha)003:846: phyag mtshan phyag na mar me bsnams //
NK029(ha)003:847: a lo ke'i dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)003:848: badz+ra a lo ke a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK029(ha)003:849: byang shar lha mo gan+d+he ma //
NK029(ha)003:851: phyag ma tshan phyag na dri chab bsnams //
NK029(ha)003:852: gan+he ma yi dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)003:853: badz+ra g+han+te a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK029(ha)003:854: shar phyogs skyong ba'i sgo ma ni //
NK029(ha)003:856: phyag mtshan phyag na lcags kyu bsnams //
NK029(ha)003:857: shar gyi sgo ma'i dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)003:858: badz+ra ang+gu sha a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK029(ha)003:859: lho phyogs skyong ba'i sgo ma ni //
NK029(ha)003:861: phyag mtshan phyag na zhags pa bsnams //
NK029(ha)003:862: lho yi sgo ma'i dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)003:863: badz+ra pa sha a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK029(ha)003:864: nub phyogs skyong ba'i sgo ma ni /
NK029(ha)003:866: phyag mtshan phyag na lcags sgrogs bsnams //
NK029(ha)003:867: nub kyi sgo ma'i dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)003:870: byang phyogs skyong ba'i sgo ma ni //
NK029(ha)003:872: phyag mtshan phyag na dril bu bsnams //
NK029(ha)003:873: byang gi sgo ma'i dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)003:877: stim gnas ni phung po khams dang skye mched la stim /
NK029(ha)003:878: sgrib pa gang dag nus pa gang skye ni /
NK029(ha)003:879: phung khams skye mched dngos po dang mtshan mar 'dzin pa'i dri ma dag nas /
NK029(ha)003:880: phung po khams skye mched rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor du
NK029(ha)003:881: lhun gyis grub pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur
NK029(ha)003:882: cig / yo ga'i dbang gi bkra shis drug cu rtsa gnyis las /
NK029(ha)003:883: dang po thugs rje gzung kyi dbang bcu gcig /
NK029(ha)003:884: dang po sku gzugs phyag rgya'i dbang ni //
NK029(ha)003:885: sngon ri rab ri'i rtse mor rin po che dang /
NK029(ha)003:887: dpal kun rig rnam pa snang mdzad kyi 'khor gyis
NK029(ha)003:888: byang chub sems dpa' don thams cad grub pa la
NK029(ha)003:889: sogs ba la / phyag rgya chen po lngas dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)003:890: rigs lnga ye shes lnga ru mthar phyin pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK029(ha)003:891: de dang rjes su mthun par phyag rgya chen po
NK029(ha)003:892: lnga'i dbang bskur bas ye shes lnga mthar phyin nas
NK029(ha)003:893: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)003:894: byang chub mchog dang sa gnon ni //
NK029(ha)003:895: mchod sbyin mnyam pa'i phyag rgyar ldan //
NK029(ha)003:896: skyabs kyi phyag rgya la sogs lngas //
NK029(ha)003:897: mi 'da' phyag rgya'i dbang thob shog /
NK029(ha)003:898: rgyal po phyag rgya mchog gi rgyas //
NK029(ha)003:899: phyag rgya'i dbang mchog mi 'da' ba //
NK029(ha)003:900: ye shes lnga dang rigs lnga'i dbang //
NK029(ha)003:901: dbang gnyis rdzogs pa'i bkra shis le'u ste bzhi bcu zhe bdun pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:902: gnyis pa gsung gi gzungs yig 'bru'i dbang ni /
NK029(ha)003:903: sngon bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad kyi 'khor
NK029(ha)003:904: rnams la snying po sngags kyis dbang bskur ba ni
NK029(ha)003:905: / rtog pa'i ye shes phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan par gyur to //
NK029(ha)003:906: de dang rjes su mthun par de bzhin gshegs pa'i
NK029(ha)003:907: thugs ye shes kyi byin gyis rlabs pa'i snying po
NK029(ha)003:909: rtog pa ye shes phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)003:910: thugs kyi sa bon 'bru mchog ste //
NK029(ha)003:911: sngags kyi byin rlabs bsam mi khyab //
NK029(ha)003:912: ye shes thugs kyi sa bon mchog /'bras bu sngags kyi bkra shis shog /
NK029(ha)003:913: snying po rigs lnga sangs rgyas gsung gi mchog /
NK029(ha)003:914: gsung mchog sngags kyi phyag rgya chen po ste //
NK029(ha)003:915: byin rlabs chen po gzhan na med pa yis //'di
NK029(ha)003:916: ni dbang rnams thob pa'i dbang gi bkra shis le'u
NK029(ha)003:921: a mi ta ba h+r+aih a mo g+ha sad+hi a /
NK029(ha)003:922: gsum pa thugs kyi gzungs gser thur ni /
NK029(ha)003:923: sngon ri rab ri'i rtse mor rnam par snang mdzad
NK029(ha)003:924: kyi 'khor rnams la gser gyi thur mas dbang bskur
NK029(ha)003:925: bas / ma rig pa'i ling thog byang nas shes rab kyi mig gsal bar gyur to //
NK029(ha)003:926: de dang rjes su mthun par gser gyi thur mas dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)003:927: ma rig pa'i ling thog byang nas shes rab kyi mig gsal bar gyur to //
NK029(ha)003:928: gser gyi thur ma thogs byas ste //
NK029(ha)003:929: mig mkhan rgyal pos dbang bskur bzhin //
NK029(ha)003:930: bu khyod ma rig mi shes pa'i //
NK029(ha)003:931: rab rib rgyal ba rnams kyi bsal //
NK029(ha)003:933: rin chen gser gyi thur ma yis //'bar ba'i ye shes gsal phye nas //
NK029(ha)003:934: nges par legs pa'i dgongs pa 'grub //
NK029(ha)003:935: shes rab mchog gi dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste bzhi bcu zhe dgu pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:936: bzhi pa me long gi dbang ni /
NK029(ha)003:937: sngon ri rab ri'i rtser rnam par snang mdzad kyi 'khor rnams la me long gis dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)003:938: chos thams cad gzugs rnyan rten 'brel sgyu ma tsam du mthong par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)003:939: chos thams cad snang la rang bzhin med par gyur to //
NK029(ha)003:940: de dang rjes su mthun par me long gi dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)003:941: chos thams cad gzugs rnyan lta bu ste //
NK029(ha)003:942: rten 'brel mthu las snang ba'i phyir //
NK029(ha)003:943: brjod med rang bzhin dag pa'i don //
NK029(ha)003:944: chos nyid sgyu ma lta bur gsal zhing ston par shog /
NK029(ha)003:945: snang gsal dri ma sel ba dang //
NK029(ha)003:946: mi mngon dbang po gsal ba dang //
NK029(ha)003:947: ye shes gsal ba'i me long gis //'di ni me
NK029(ha)003:948: long gsal gyi bkra shis le'u ste lnga bcu pa'o
NK029(ha)003:950: sngon ri rab ri'i rtser rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la 'khor los dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)003:951: 'gro ba'i don la thag thog med par gyur to //
NK029(ha)003:952: de dang rjes su mthun par 'khor los dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)003:953: 'khor ba'i rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa dang ldan nas /
NK029(ha)003:954: khams gsum gyi gnas thams cad du 'gro ba'i don
NK029(ha)003:955: la thag thog med par 'gro bar gyur cig /'og
NK029(ha)003:957: brjod pa med don 'bru bkod nas //
NK029(ha)003:958: gzhan gyi don la phan pa'i phyir //
NK029(ha)003:959: rgyal ba'i 'khor lo bskor bar shog /
NK029(ha)003:960: nyon mongs me'i gzhom pa dang //
NK029(ha)003:961: legs pa'i yon tan rdzogs pa dang //'bras bu kun tu 'phags pa'i phyir //
NK029(ha)003:962: des ni dbang rnams bkra shis le'u ste nga gcig pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:964: sngon bcom ldan 'das la lha'i rgyal po dbang po
NK029(ha)003:965: brgya byin gyis dung gtsug g.yas su 'khyil ba phul
NK029(ha)003:966: bas rdo rje spo la gshegs ste chos sgra chen
NK029(ha)003:967: pos gsung dbyangs yan lag drug cu dang ldan pa'i
NK029(ha)003:968: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i rdzas 'dis /
NK029(ha)003:969: ngas slob ma rnams la sbyin pas /
NK029(ha)003:970: tshangs pa'i sgra skad phun sum tshogs shing /
NK029(ha)003:971: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i don gyi bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)003:972: dung gi chos kyi sgra rnams sgrogs pa'i tshul //
NK029(ha)003:973: yon tan rgya mtsho bdag nyid mchog gyur nas //
NK029(ha)003:974: rnam dag chos la thogs med longs spyod pa'i //
NK029(ha)003:975: bkra shis des ni tshig la longs spyod shog /
NK029(ha)003:976: chos sgra chen po phyogs bcur grags pa dang //
NK029(ha)003:977: rgyal ba'i gsung mchog dung gi sgra bus ste //
NK029(ha)003:978: ma lus rgyal ba kun gyi rgyud 'grol ba //'di
NK029(ha)003:979: ni 'phags pa'i gsung gi dbang gi bkra shis le'u
NK029(ha)003:981: bdun pa me tog 'phreng ba'i dbang ni /
NK029(ha)003:982: sngon bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la //
NK029(ha)003:983: me tog gi 'phreng bas dbang bskur bas //
NK029(ha)003:984: tshul khrims kyi 'phreng ba yongs su rdzogs par gyur to //
NK029(ha)003:985: de dang rjes su mthun par /
NK029(ha)003:986: me tog gi 'phreng bas dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)003:987: tshul khrims gyi 'phreng bas yongs su rdzogs pas /
NK029(ha)003:988: ngan song las ldog pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)003:989: sdug cing mdzes pa'i me tog brgyan //
NK029(ha)003:990: dgos pa'i don rnams myur bar 'byin //
NK029(ha)003:991: thams cad kun gyi yid du 'ong //'byor ba'i longs spyod brgyan du shog /
NK029(ha)003:992: kha dog dbyibs legs rin chen me tog 'di //
NK029(ha)003:993: nam mkha' gang zhing sa gzhi khebs pa yis //
NK029(ha)003:994: mchod pa'i phrin phung dus su char 'bab pa'i //'di
NK029(ha)003:995: ni me tog mdzes pa'i dbang gi bkra shis le'u
NK029(ha)003:997: brgyad pa 'phrin las rdo rje'i dbang /
NK029(ha)003:998: sngon ri rab ri'i rtser rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la /
NK029(ha)003:999: phyag rgya bzhi la rdo rje res dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)003:1000: thugs rdo rje rigs kyi dbang dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK029(ha)003:1001: de dang rjes su mthun par phyag rgya bzhi la rdo rje res dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)003:1002: thugs ye shes rdo rje lta bu'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)003:1003: sku yi phyag rgya rtags brtan pa //
NK029(ha)003:1004: ye shes rdo rje lta bu de //
NK029(ha)003:1005: rdo rje thugs kyi rang bzhin ni //
NK029(ha)003:1006: me tog lta bu'i ye shes thob par shog /
NK029(ha)003:1007: rdo rje rigs mchog rdo rje sems dpa' che //
NK029(ha)003:1008: dkar la dag pa shar phyogs sangs rgyas zhing //
NK029(ha)003:1009: bde ba chen po'i brgyan du bstan pa yis //
NK029(ha)003:1010: thugs kyi bkris le'u ste lnga bcu nga bzhi pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:1012: sngon ri rab ri'i rtser dpal kun rig rnam par snang mdzad kyis /
NK029(ha)003:1013: 'khor rnams la phyag rgya chen po bzhi'i rin po che'i dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)003:1014: yon tan rin po che'i rigs dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)003:1015: de dang rjes su mthun par phyag rgya rin po ches dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)003:1016: yon tan rin po che lta bu dang ldan pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)003:1017: sku yi phyag rgya rtags rtan nas //'gro ba kun gyi re ba bskongs //
NK029(ha)003:1018: yon tan rin chen rang bzhin ste //
NK029(ha)003:1019: mnyam nyid ye shes thob par shog /
NK029(ha)003:1020: rin chen rigs mchog sems dpa' ste //
NK029(ha)003:1021: sngo la dag pas lho phyogs sangs rgyas zhing //
NK029(ha)003:1022: bde ba chen po'i bstan pa ni //
NK029(ha)003:1023: yon tan bkra shis le'u ste nga lnga pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:1025: sngon ri rab rtser dpal rnam par snang mdzad kyis //'khor rnams la pad+ma'i dbang bskur bas //
NK029(ha)003:1026: pad+ma gsung gi rigs kyi dbang dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK029(ha)003:1027: de dang rjes su mthun par phyag rgya chen po bzhi la pad+ma'i dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)003:1028: 'gro ba'i don mdzad pas nyes pa'i skyon gyis ma
NK029(ha)003:1029: gos pa'i gsung dam pa lta bu dang ldan pa'i
NK029(ha)003:1030: dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)003:1031: sku yi phyag rgya rtags bstan pa //
NK029(ha)003:1032: pad+ma dbang gi rang bzhin ste /
NK029(ha)003:1033: gsung gi rang bzhin 'byung ba'i mdzod //
NK029(ha)003:1034: so sor rtogs pa'i ye shes thob par shog /
NK029(ha)003:1035: pad+ma rigs mchog chos kyi sems dpa' ste //
NK029(ha)003:1036: dmar la dag pa nub phyogs bde chen zhing //
NK029(ha)003:1037: bde ba chen po'i brgyan du bstan pa yis //
NK029(ha)003:1038: gsung gi bkra shis ste nga drug pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:1039: bcu gcig pa rdo rje rgya gram gyi dbang /
NK029(ha)003:1040: sngon ri rab ri yi rtse mor dpal rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la /
NK029(ha)003:1041: phyag rgya bzhi las rdo rje brgya gram gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)003:1042: thugs rdo rje rigs kyi dbang dam pa thob par gyur te /
NK029(ha)003:1043: de dang rjes su mthun par phyag rgya chen po bzhi las rdo rje'i dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)003:1044: thugs ye shes rdo rje lta bu dang ldan pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)003:1045: sku yi phyag rgya rtags bstan pa //
NK029(ha)003:1046: ye shes rdo rje lta bu ste //
NK029(ha)003:1047: rdo rje thugs kyi rang bzhin ni //
NK029(ha)003:1048: me long ye shes thob par shog /
NK029(ha)003:1049: rdo rje rigs mchog rdo rje sems dpa' ste //
NK029(ha)003:1050: dkar la dag pas shar phyogs sangs rgyas zhing //
NK029(ha)003:1051: bde ba chen po'i brgyan du bstan pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:1052: thugs dbang bkra shis le'u nga bdun pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:1053: lnga pa khyad par gdan gyi dbang la gsum las /
NK029(ha)003:1054: dang po zil gnon seng ge'i dbang /
NK029(ha)003:1055: sngon ri rab ri yi rtser dpa' rnam par snang
NK029(ha)003:1056: mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la seng ge'i dbang bskur bas
NK029(ha)003:1057: / log pa'i phyogs zil gyis non pa'i dbang thob par gyur to //
NK029(ha)003:1058: de dang rjes su mthun par seng ge'i dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)003:1059: gsung rabs rgya mtsho'i sgras log pa'i phyogs thams cad zil gyis mnan nas /
NK029(ha)003:1060: skad cig la stong spyi phud kyi sems can mngon
NK029(ha)003:1061: par rdzogs par sangs rgya bar byed pa'i bcom ldan
NK029(ha)003:1062: 'das dpal kun tu bzang po zhes bya bar gyur
NK029(ha)003:1063: cig / gdug bzang sems can kun gyi gtso bo ste //
NK029(ha)003:1064: zil gnon sgra 'byin sder chags skrag par byed //
NK029(ha)003:1065: phyogs rnams kun bskyed seng ge dpal dang ldan //
NK029(ha)003:1066: zil gyis gnon pa'i dbang rnams thob par shog /
NK029(ha)003:1067: seng ge nga ro sgra chen thog med pas //'jigs med 'joms pa'i sgra rnams bsgrag nas kyang //
NK029(ha)003:1068: bdud kyi dpung rnams zil gyis gnon mdzad pa'i //
NK029(ha)003:1069: mthu dpung che ba'i bkra shis nga brgyad pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:1070: gnyis pa mun sel nyi ma'i dbang /
NK029(ha)003:1071: sngon ri rab ri'i rtser rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la nyi ma'i dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)003:1072: ma rig pa'i mun pa sel ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK029(ha)003:1073: de dang rjes su mthun par nyi ma'i dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)003:1074: skye 'gro ma lus pa'i sems kyi rgyud la ye
NK029(ha)003:1075: shes kyi 'od zer chen po'i dus mtha' med par
NK029(ha)003:1076: 'char ba'i skal ba dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)003:1077: nyi ma mun sel shes rab sgron //
NK029(ha)003:1078: kun las gsal bas rin po che //
NK029(ha)003:1079: thams cad kun gyi dpal du shar //
NK029(ha)003:1080: ma rig sel ba'i sgron mar shog /
NK029(ha)003:1081: ye shes gsal bas phyogs bcur khyab par dro //
NK029(ha)003:1082: thugs rje che bas mun sel byed //'od gsal dra bas 'gro ba'i don mdzad pas //
NK029(ha)003:1083: shes rab bkra shis le'u nga dgu pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:1084: gsum pa zla ba'i dbang ni /
NK029(ha)003:1085: sngon ri rab ri'i rtser rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la zla bas dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)003:1086: mun pa sel zhing tsha ba'i sdug bsngal sel ba'i dbang thob par gyur to //
NK029(ha)003:1087: de dang rjes su mthun par zla ba lag tu
NK029(ha)003:1088: byin pas stong khams thams cad kyi mun pa dus
NK029(ha)003:1089: cig tu byang nas kun tu gsal bar byed par
NK029(ha)003:1090: gyur cig / thams cad kun gsal chu shel lta bu ste //
NK029(ha)003:1091: dgongs pa'i don 'byin dkar la dag pa'i tshul //
NK029(ha)003:1092: tshad med thabs kyi zla ba rin po che //
NK029(ha)003:1093: ma rig mun sel dbang mchog bkra shis shog /
NK029(ha)003:1094: dkar la dag pa zla ba dri med pas //
NK029(ha)003:1095: thabs kyi mtshan nyid skyon gyis ma gos ste //
NK029(ha)003:1096: yongs su dag pas mun sel bsil ba'i sman //
NK029(ha)003:1097: thabs dbang bkra shis le'u drug cu pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:1098: bzhi pa shes rab ye shes kyi dbang ni //
NK029(ha)003:1099: sngon dpal rnam par snang mdzad kyis bdud rtsi bum pa'i 'khor rnams la dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)003:1100: rnam par rtog pa sel bar gyur to //
NK029(ha)003:1101: de dang rjes su mthun par de bzhin gshegs pa'i
NK029(ha)003:1102: thugs rjes byin gyis rlabs pa'i bdud rtsi bum pas
NK029(ha)003:1103: dbang bskur bas lus dang khong mi bde ba'i nad
NK029(ha)003:1104: rnams bkrus nas dag cing byang bar gyur cig /
NK029(ha)003:1105: spros med spros bral chos kyi dbyings //
NK029(ha)003:1106: bum pa zlum po yum gyi gter //
NK029(ha)003:1107: phan byed sman pa'i mchog yin ste //'gro ba'i nad sel bkra shis shog /
NK029(ha)003:1108: bum pa zlum po spros med chos kyi dbyings //
NK029(ha)003:1109: thugs rje chen pos phan mdzad yum gyi tshul //'khor ba'i gnas skyob dri ma dag mdzad pa //
NK029(ha)003:1110: sgrib sel bkra shis le'u re gcig pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:1111: drug pa rgyal srid rin po che'i dbang la bcu drug las /
NK029(ha)003:1113: 'khor los bsgyur 'khor lo rin po che'i tshul ji lta bu dang ldan zhes na /
NK029(ha)003:1114: rgyal po rgyal rigs spyi bo nas dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)003:1115: gso sbyong gi nyi ma bco lnga la dbu khrus byas la /
NK029(ha)003:1117: steng gi 'khyams btsun mo'i 'khor na gnas pa'i tshe /
NK029(ha)003:1118: shar phyogs nas 'khor lo rtsibs stong yod pa /
NK029(ha)003:1119: lte ba dang mu khyud gser las grub pa /
NK029(ha)003:1120: 'gar gzos ma byas shing rang byung ba /
NK029(ha)003:1121: gnam 'phangs su rta la bdun gyi srid tsam zhig
NK029(ha)003:1122: rgyal po'i phyag g.yas pa'i mthil du rang babs ste
NK029(ha)003:1123: / de'i tshe rgyal po'i bsam pas rtags 'di dang
NK029(ha)003:1124: sbyar na bdag ni 'khor los bsgyur ba'i rgyal po
NK029(ha)003:1125: yin nges so snyam nas lag pa g.yas pas 'khor
NK029(ha)003:1126: / lo bskor ste / rdzu 'phrul gyi nam mkha' la 'gro zhing phyag du 'khor lo gnas ste /
NK029(ha)003:1127: rgyal ba gsung gi tshogs dang bcas pa yang gnas pa ru 'khod de /
NK029(ha)003:1128: gling bzhi la gnas pa'i rgyal rigs thams cad kyis mdun bsu zhing gnas pa'i tshe /
NK029(ha)003:1129: mi thams cad dge bcu'i lam la 'khor cing 'dzud par byed la /
NK029(ha)003:1130: nang par khes su sus la dga' ba nyams su myong bar byed do //
NK029(ha)003:1131: de dang rjes su mthun par 'khor lo rin po ches dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)003:1132: ming 'di la chos kyi 'khor lo rin chen bskor
NK029(ha)003:1133: te 'jig rten gsum gyi 'gro ba mus pa rnams
NK029(ha)003:1134: rnam par grol ba'i lam la 'god cing so so'i
NK029(ha)003:1135: skal pa ci lta ba bzhin du sems kyi rgyud
NK029(ha)003:1136: la yongs su smin par byed cing /
NK029(ha)003:1137: 'khor los bsgyur ba'i rgyal srid kyi dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)003:1138: dus gsum rgyal bas bskor ba'i 'khor lo 'di //
NK029(ha)003:1139: mi kho ma rgyun chad rgyu dang 'bras bur ston //'khor los bsgyur ba'i dbang phyug rin po chen //
NK029(ha)003:1140: bla med 'khor lo dam pa bskor gyur cig /
NK029(ha)003:1141: stong nyid ye shes gsal ba'i 'khor lo la //
NK029(ha)003:1142: chos nyid dbyings las 'phrin las cir yang ston //
NK029(ha)003:1143: sems can kha lo gyen du bsgyur mdzad pa //
NK029(ha)003:1144: chos 'khor bskor ba'i bkra shis le'u ste re gnyis pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:1145: gnyis pa rta mchog dbang ni /
NK029(ha)003:1146: 'khor lo bsgyur ba'i rta mchog rin po che'i tshul ji lta bu dang ldan zhe na /
NK029(ha)003:1147: mdog rin chen in tra ni la ltar sngon por gnas pa /
NK029(ha)003:1148: rngog ma ljang lor gnas pa /
NK029(ha)003:1149: zhon nas gus par byed pa /
NK029(ha)003:1150: gser gser gyis brgyan pa gser gyi dra bas g.yogs
NK029(ha)003:1151: pa rdzu 'phrul dang ldan pa zhig nam mkha' la
NK029(ha)003:1155: rgyal pos nyi ma shar bar rta la zhon ste /
NK029(ha)003:1156: gling bzhi'i rgya mtsho mtha' bskor ste /
NK029(ha)003:1157: slar log pa dang khye'u gzugs kyi dga' ba nyams su myong /
NK029(ha)003:1158: de dang rjes su mthun par rta rin po ches dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)003:1159: ming 'di zhes bya ba rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi dang ldan de /
NK029(ha)003:1160: bzhon pa dang ldan nas thams cad dga' 'gu 'gro
NK029(ha)003:1161: ba la thogs pa med par gyur cig /'khor ba'i
NK029(ha)003:1162: chu bo 'jig pa bzhi las grol //
NK029(ha)003:1163: brtson 'grus myur bas rdzu 'phrul shugs kyi 'gro //
NK029(ha)003:1164: cang shes sprin gyis shugs 'chang rin po che //
NK029(ha)003:1165: mi gnas yid bzhin spyod par shog /
NK029(ha)003:1166: rdzu 'phrul thogs med kun tu myur ba'i shugs //
NK029(ha)003:1167: gar yang 'gro ba'i don la myur ba dang //
NK029(ha)003:1168: rdzu 'phrul sna tshogs kun tu ston pa yi //
NK029(ha)003:1169: thogs med dbang gi bkra shis le'u re gsum pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:1171: 'khor los bsgyur ba'i rgyal po glang po rin po che'i tshul ji lta bu ldan zhes na /
NK029(ha)003:1172: kha dog shel cag pa'i 'phro bzhin du dkar ba /
NK029(ha)003:1173: yan lag bdun du shin tu gnas pa /
NK029(ha)003:1174: rin po che gtsug gis shin tu brgyan pa /
NK029(ha)003:1175: gser gyi dra bas shin tu brgyan pa /
NK029(ha)003:1176: rdzu 'phrul dang ldan shing nam mkha' la 'gro ba /
NK029(ha)003:1177: lha dang lha ma yin gyis g.yul rab tu 'gyed pa na /
NK029(ha)003:1178: g.yul de dag la rab tu rgyal ba'i mthu dang ldan pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:1179: de dang rjes su mthun par glang po che 'di byin pas /
NK029(ha)003:1180: rdo ba'i phyogs thams cad zil gyi gnon pa'i mthu dang ldan zhing rgyal bar gyur cig /
NK029(ha)003:1181: theg pa'i don de bla med bstod pa'i mchog /
NK029(ha)003:1182: yan lag bdun mdzes u mu ta'i mdog /'dul dka' stobs chen glang po rin po che /
NK029(ha)003:1183: khyu mchog rlabs chen stobs lnga rdzogs par shog /
NK029(ha)003:1184: stobs mchog pha rol gnon pa'i stobs mnga' ba //
NK029(ha)003:1185: gdug pa chen po gzhan gyis mi non pa'i //
NK029(ha)003:1186: pha rol gzhan gyi rdzu 'phrul non mdzad pa //
NK029(ha)003:1187: mthu stobs dbang gi bkra shis ste le'u re bzhi pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:1188: bzhi pa nor bu rin po che'i dbang ni /
NK029(ha)003:1189: nor bu rin po che'i tshul ji lta bu dang ldan zhes na /
NK029(ha)003:1190: thams cad du sngon bee t+aur+ya'i rang bzhin du gnas pa /
NK029(ha)003:1192: yon tan stong dang ldan pa byung ste /
NK029(ha)003:1193: shin tu sbyang ba de nam gyi gung la mun pa rab tu gnag pa la /
NK029(ha)003:1194: nyams sad pa'i phyir rgyal mtshan gyi rtse mo la btags te /
NK029(ha)003:1196: skyed mo 'tshal du gzigs mo'i rnam pa thams cad lta bar 'dod na yang /
NK029(ha)003:1197: nor bu rin po che'i 'od kyi dpung gis tshogs
NK029(ha)003:1198: yan lag bzhi yan chad dpag tshad gcig tshun chad
NK029(ha)003:1199: gang dgar mthong par gyur to //
NK029(ha)003:1201: de dang rjes su mthun par non bu rin po che 'di byin pas /
NK029(ha)003:1202: shes rab rnam par dag pa dang ldan ste /
NK029(ha)003:1203: kun nas nyon mongs par gyur pa'i mun pa thams
NK029(ha)003:1204: cad gsal ba'i sgron me dang ldan nas lhag mthong
NK029(ha)003:1205: gi ye shes rin po che dang ldan par gyur
NK029(ha)003:1206: cig / dkon mchog gsum gyi yon tan yid bzhin
NK029(ha)003:1207: gter //'khor ba'i mun sel bde ba'i snying po 'byung
NK029(ha)003:1208: cig / // dgongs pa mchod sbyin nor bdun phun sum tshogs //
NK029(ha)003:1209: yid bzhin nor bu rin chen spyod par shog /
NK029(ha)003:1210: dgos 'dod bskong ba'i nor bu rin po che //
NK029(ha)003:1211: thams cad kun gyis yid dang mthun par shog che ba'i yon tan phun sum tshogs pa yis //
NK029(ha)003:1212: yid bzhin bkra shis le'u ste re lnga pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:1213: lnga pa blon po rin po che'i dbang ni /
NK029(ha)003:1214: blon po rin po che'i tshul ji lta bu dang ldan zhes na /
NK029(ha)003:1219: dpag tshad tshun chad du rin po che'i gter yod pa mthong ste /
NK029(ha)003:1220: rin po che'i gter chu'i nang na yod pa dang /
NK029(ha)003:1222: ring ba na yod pa dang //
NK029(ha)003:1224: bdag po med pa thams cad mthong ste /
NK029(ha)003:1225: des 'khor los bsgyur ba'i rgyal po la gsol pa /
NK029(ha)003:1226: lha dkon nor la thugs khral chung bar mdzod cig /
NK029(ha)003:1227: dkor nor ci bzhed par ni ci bzhed pa bka' stsol cig /
NK029(ha)003:1228: de skad ces gsol pa dang /
NK029(ha)003:1229: rgyal po'i dgongs pa thams cad bsgrub po /
NK029(ha)003:1230: de dang rjes su mthun par blon po rin po che 'dis dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)003:1231: ming 'di zhes bya ba la lha'i mig rnam par 'phags pa'i nor bdun dang ldan zhing /
NK029(ha)003:1232: bdag dang gzhan gyi don phun sum tshogs pa'i dgos pa thams cad mthar phyin pa dang /
NK029(ha)003:1233: shes bya la thog pa med pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)003:1234: gang la ci 'dod dpag bsam shing lta bu //'gro la snying brtse tshogs gnyis rdzogs par smon //
NK029(ha)003:1235: dbang phyug blon po'i nor bu rin po che //'khor
NK029(ha)003:1236: los bsgyur ba'i rgyal thabs thob par shog /'dzangs pa'i
NK029(ha)003:1237: phul phyin blon po rin po che //
NK029(ha)003:1238: legs nyes kun mkhas spyod pa'i don la mkhas /
NK029(ha)003:1239: yo khal do srong 'dzangs pa'i 'phrul bag can //
NK029(ha)003:1240: blon po dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste re drug pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:1241: bdun pa btsun mo rin po che'i dbang /
NK029(ha)003:1242: 'khor los bsgyur ba'i btsun mo rin po che tshul ji lta bu zhe na /
NK029(ha)003:1243: rgyal po rgyal rigs su skyes pa /
NK029(ha)003:1249: mi'i mdog las 'das nas tshul lha'i mdog thob ste /
NK029(ha)003:1250: lpags pa'i mdog kyang spri yang ku ltar 'dug pa /
NK029(ha)003:1251: lus ran cing dbyibs legs pa /
NK029(ha)003:1252: sha ran cing ba spu'i bu ga nas tsan dan dri bsung dang ldan pa /
NK029(ha)003:1254: kha nas u dpal gyi ngad ldang ba /
NK029(ha)003:1255: lus kyang bya ka tsha li ka ltar reg na bde ba /
NK029(ha)003:1256: drang ba'i dus na reg na dro ba /
NK029(ha)003:1257: tsha ba'i dus na reg na bsil ba de ni sngon du bya ba dang /
NK029(ha)003:1258: phyi nas ci bya ba'i lung ma nor ba yid du 'ong bar byed pa /
NK029(ha)003:1259: snyan par smra ba la mkhas te /
NK029(ha)003:1260: yid kyi dgu la yang 'khor los bsgyur ba'i rgyal po yid dang 'gal bar mi byed na /
NK029(ha)003:1261: lus dang ngag gi dang ga la byed de /
NK029(ha)003:1262: des ni bud med thams cad kyi skyon sel ba ste /
NK029(ha)003:1263: dpen na skar ma spa ba sangs kyi skar ma thams cad zil gyis non pa bzhin no //
NK029(ha)003:1264: de dang rjes su mthun par btsun mo rin po che 'di byin pas /
NK029(ha)003:1265: ming 'di zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin zhi ba'i chos la dbang 'byor ste /
NK029(ha)003:1266: 'phags pa'i 'jig rten las 'das pa'i lam spyod /
NK029(ha)003:1267: yul yongs su dag pas bdag dang gzhan gyi don bden par sdud pa la yid bzhin 'du /
NK029(ha)003:1268: 'byor ba la dpal dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)003:1269: pha rol phyin bcu skyob pa'i phyir //
NK029(ha)003:1270: shes rab gzung 'dzin btsun mo rin mo che //
NK029(ha)003:1271: bsdu ba rnam bzhi tshad med bzhi po yi //
NK029(ha)003:1272: tshe dang longs spyod gter rnams spyod par shog /
NK029(ha)003:1273: shes rab dbyings las sprul pa'i lha //
NK029(ha)003:1274: dgos pa'i don 'grub btsun mo ste /
NK029(ha)003:1275: mthu dang dad pas 'brel pa yis //
NK029(ha)003:1276: btsun mo'i bkra shis le'u re bdun pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:1277: bdun pa dmag dpon rin po che'i dbang /
NK029(ha)003:1278: dmag dpon rin po che'i tshul ci lta bu zhes na /
NK029(ha)003:1283: rgyal po bsam pa bzhin byed nus pa /
NK029(ha)003:1285: sgra thams cad kyi sbyor ba la mkhas pa /
NK029(ha)003:1286: bsdo ba thams cad zil gyi non pa'i go cha bgos pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:1287: de dang rjes su mthun par dmag dpon rin po
NK029(ha)003:1288: che 'di byin pas ming 'di zhes bya ba thabs
NK029(ha)003:1289: dang shes rab gnyis su med pa'i dgongs pa mthar
NK029(ha)003:1290: phyin nas / 'jigs tshogs kyi lta ba thams cad
NK029(ha)003:1291: legs par spyod pa'i ye shes phun sum tshogs pa
NK029(ha)003:1293: gnod pa'i dpung 'joms brtson 'grus go bgos ste //'jigs pa'i skyabs byed 'gro la ma 'jigs sbyin //
NK029(ha)003:1294: thabs dang shes rab bstan pa'i dmag dpon 'di //
NK029(ha)003:1295: mthu stobs rdzu 'phrul dpung gis bsrungs bar shog /
NK029(ha)003:1296: drag shul dreg pas pha rol 'joms mdzad pa //
NK029(ha)003:1297: nyon mongs mi shes g.yul ngo sel ba yis /
NK029(ha)003:1298: rnam par rtog pa cis kyang mi tshugs pa'i /
NK029(ha)003:1299: gnyen po 'dul ba'i le'u ste re brgyad pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:1300: brgyad pa ral gri'i dbang ni /
NK029(ha)003:1301: sngon ri rab ri'i rtser rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la ral gris dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)003:1302: nyon mongs pa'i dra ba gcod pa'i dbang thob par gyur to //
NK029(ha)003:1303: de dang rjes su mthun par ye shes kyi gral du phyin pas //
NK029(ha)003:1304: sdug bsngal gyi rgyu 'khrul pa bcad pas bag chags thams cad yongs su byang bar gyur cig /
NK029(ha)003:1305: sgrib pa'i dra ba bcad nas kyang /
NK029(ha)003:1306: mi shes dra ba gcod tshul du rnon pos bag gcod pa ste /
NK029(ha)003:1307: thams cad kun las rgyal bar shog /
NK029(ha)003:1308: sgrib pa sdig pa'i dra ba gcod mdzad pa //
NK029(ha)003:1309: ye shes rnon po gar yang thog pa med //
NK029(ha)003:1310: ye shes bag chags rtsad nas gcod mdzad pa'i //
NK029(ha)003:1311: sdug bsngal gcod pa'i bkra shis le'u ste re dgu pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:1313: sngon ri rab ri'i rtser dpal rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la 'da' gzhu'i dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)003:1314: thabs dang shes rab kyi dbang thob po //
NK029(ha)003:1315: de dang rjes su mthun par 'da' gzhus dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)003:1316: thabs dang shes rab rnam par thar pa'i rgya mtsho myur du bgrod par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)003:1317: bsdo ba'i phyogs 'joms myur ba'i shugs 'chang ba'i //
NK029(ha)003:1318: thabs kyi 'dul la nyes pas ma gos ste /
NK029(ha)003:1319: dngos po kun 'joms pha rol 'bigs pa ste //
NK029(ha)003:1320: thabs kyi 'dul ba'i dbang mchog dam pa thob par shog /
NK029(ha)003:1321: thabs dang shes rab dbyer med gcig pa yis //
NK029(ha)003:1322: thugs rje myur ba'i thabs kyis 'gro la 'byung /
NK029(ha)003:1323: yang rab brtsal mchog blo yi rnon po ste //
NK029(ha)003:1324: shes rab thog med bkra shis le'u bdun cu pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:1325: bcu pa rnam ral gri dbang ni /
NK029(ha)003:1326: sngon dpal rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la rnam ral rin po che'i dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)003:1327: bar du 'joms pa'i bdud dpung 'joms pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)003:1328: stobs ldan dbang phyug mthu stobs che mnga' ba //
NK029(ha)003:1329: bdud dpung phas kyi sdo ba kun btul nas //
NK029(ha)003:1330: che ba chen pos kun la rgyal ba dang //
NK029(ha)003:1331: thams cad mthu stobs kun las dbang byed shog /
NK029(ha)003:1332: rin chen brgyad mdzes rnam ral rin po che //
NK029(ha)003:1333: log pa'i phyogs dang bsdo ba zil gnon pa //
NK029(ha)003:1334: thabs la mkhas pa'i bdud dpung che ba ste //
NK029(ha)003:1335: kun las rgyal ba'i bkra shis le'u don gcig pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:1336: bcu gcig pa shan gri'i dbang ni /
NK029(ha)003:1337: sngon ri rab ri'i rtser dpal rnam par snang mdzad
NK029(ha)003:1338: kyis 'khor rnams la bshan gri nye ba'i rin po
NK029(ha)003:1340: 'khor ba'i sgrib pa gcod pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK029(ha)003:1341: de dang rjes su mthun par bshan nye ba'i rin po ches dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)003:1342: 'khor ba'i sgrib pa'i dra ba gcod pa dang /
NK029(ha)003:1343: dngos po mtshan ma gzhom pa dang /
NK029(ha)003:1344: mi shes rnam rtog ma lus bsgral ba'i phyir /
NK029(ha)003:1345: bdug pa 'joms pa'i dbang rnams thob par shog /
NK029(ha)003:1346: rin chen mdzes pa'i bshan mchog rin po che /
NK029(ha)003:1347: legs par rno la pha rol nyes pa gcod //
NK029(ha)003:1348: ye shes rnon po kun gyi yid du 'ong //
NK029(ha)003:1349: sdug bsngal gcod pa'i bkra shis le'u ste don gnyis pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:1350: bcu gnyis pa zhwa'i dbang ni /
NK029(ha)003:1351: sngon ri rab ri'i rtser kun rig rnam par snang mdzad kyis /
NK029(ha)003:1352: 'khor la zhwa'i nye ba'i rin po ches dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)003:1353: bgegs dang logs 'dre med pa'i tshe'i dbang thob par gyur to //
NK029(ha)003:1354: de dang rjes su mthun par zhwa nye ba'i rin po ches dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)003:1355: bgegs dang leg 'dre cis kyang mi tshugs pa'i tshe'i g.yu drung gi dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)003:1357: gdung ba sel ba'i dbang mchog ste //'bras bu thar
NK029(ha)003:1358: ba thob pa'i phyir //'jigs pa bzhi yi skyabs su
NK029(ha)003:1359: shog / rin chen brgyan mchog dbu zhwa rin po
NK029(ha)003:1360: che //'jigs pa bzhi skyobs log pa'i skyon las bsrung
NK029(ha)003:1361: shog / // mi 'gyur g.yu drung tshe'i dbang thob pa //
NK029(ha)003:1362: g.yu drung bkra shis le'u ste don gsum pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:1363: bcu gsum pa khab skud dbang ni /
NK029(ha)003:1364: sngon ri rab ri'i rtser rnam par snang mdzad kyis
NK029(ha)003:1365: 'khor la tshang pa'i kha bskud kyi dbang bskur bas
NK029(ha)003:1366: / legs pa'i yon tan 'dod pa'i dbang thob par gyur to //
NK029(ha)003:1367: de dang rjes su mthun par tshangs pa'i khab skud kyis dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)003:1368: legs pa'i yon tan grub pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)003:1369: tshangs pa'i kha bskud nye ba'i bkra shis ste /
NK029(ha)003:1370: legs pa'i yon tan tshangs par rdzogs pa'i dpal //
NK029(ha)003:1371: nyes pa kun skyobs phyir na bkra shis ste //
NK029(ha)003:1372: thams cad rdzogs pa'i dbang mchog bkra shis shog /
NK029(ha)003:1373: tshangs pa'i khab skud legs pa'i yon tan 'grub //
NK029(ha)003:1374: gang la yid 'cham legs pa'i dgongs pa 'grub //
NK029(ha)003:1375: don la thugs rje chen po che ba'i rtags //
NK029(ha)003:1376: legs pa tshangs pa'i bkra shis le'u ste don bzhi pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:1377: bcu bzhi pa na baza'i dbang ni /
NK029(ha)003:1378: sngon ri rab ri'i rtser dpal rnam par snang mdzad
NK029(ha)003:1379: kyis 'khor rnams la na bza' nye ba'i rin po
NK029(ha)003:1381: grang ba'i sdug bsngal skyob pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK029(ha)003:1382: de dang rjes su mthun par na bza' nye ba'i rin po ches dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)003:1383: 'di dang pha rol gnyis kar grang ba'i nyon mongs
NK029(ha)003:1384: pa zhi ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig
NK029(ha)003:1385: / nyes pa kun skyob na bza' rin po ches bde mchog yid bzhin zad pa med pa ste //
NK029(ha)003:1386: yon tan tshangs pa'i na bza' dam pa 'di //'di dang pha rol gnyis su gon par shog /
NK029(ha)003:1387: rin chen na bza' ji ltar blta bar gdug /
NK029(ha)003:1388: che chung dbyibs ran 'gro la mdzes par snang //
NK029(ha)003:1389: yon tan bla med 'phags pa'i sku dang mtshungs //
NK029(ha)003:1390: chos nyid rtags kyi bkra shis le'u ste don lnga pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:1391: bco lnga pa chags kyi dbang ni /
NK029(ha)003:1392: sngon ri rab ri'i rtser dpal rnam par snang mdzad kyis /
NK029(ha)003:1393: chags nye ba'i rin po ches dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)003:1394: thugs rje 'gro ba'i don la chags pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK029(ha)003:1395: de dang rjes su mthun par chags nye ba'i rin po ches dbang bskur pas /
NK029(ha)003:1396: 'gro ba'i don la zhabs kyis 'chags dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)003:1397: rin chen chags kyis dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)003:1398: kun la snyoms pa'i thugs rje yis //
NK029(ha)003:1399: sems can don la thogs med de //'gro ba 'dren pa'i dpal du shog /
NK029(ha)003:1400: rin chen mdzes pa'i tshogs mchod dam pa rnams //
NK029(ha)003:1401: gar yang thogs med phyogs bcur bsgrod nas kyang //
NK029(ha)003:1402: don rnams ma lus rdzogs par bya ba yi //
NK029(ha)003:1403: yongs la khyab pa'i bkra shis le'u ste don drug pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:1404: bcu drug pa khri snyan sa le'i dbang ni /
NK029(ha)003:1405: sngon ri rab ri'i rtser dpal kun rig rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la /
NK029(ha)003:1406: khri gnyan sa le'i lpags pa nye ba'i rin po ches dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)003:1407: snying rjes sems can 'dren pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK029(ha)003:1408: de dang rjes su mthun par khri gnyan sa le'i
NK029(ha)003:1409: lpag pa nye ba'i rin po ches dbang bskur bas
NK029(ha)003:1410: / thugs rjes sems can gyis don byed pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)003:1411: khri gnyan sa le'i lpags pa bkra shis ste /
NK029(ha)003:1412: thams cad snyoms pa'i bkra shis dam pa ste /
NK029(ha)003:1413: yon tan tshang bar rdzogs pa'i bkra shis pa //
NK029(ha)003:1414: snying rjes don byed dbang mchog bkra shis shog /
NK029(ha)003:1415: snying rje chen pos sems can don la mkhas //
NK029(ha)003:1416: nyams thag 'phongs pas kun gyi don bya ste //
NK029(ha)003:1417: sems can 'khor ba'i gnas nas 'dren mdzad pa //'gro don rdzogasapa'i bkra shis le'u ste don bdun pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:1418: bdun pa bkra shis rdzas kyi dbang la bcu drug las /
NK029(ha)003:1419: dang po yung dkar gyi dbang ni /
NK029(ha)003:1420: sngon bcom ldan 'das kyis yungs dkar 'thor byed kyi /
NK029(ha)003:1421: rgyal bo bgegs gyi gnyen por byin gyis rlabs pa'i rdzas ni /
NK029(ha)003:1422: rdo rje slob dpon ngas byin pas /
NK029(ha)003:1423: slob ma'i lus sems kyi rgyud la /
NK029(ha)003:1424: bgegs stong phrag brgya bcu'i bsam sbyor ngan pas mi tshugs shing /
NK029(ha)003:1425: bgegs thams cad 'dul ba'i mthu stobs phun sum tshogs pa'i don gyi bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)003:1426: yungs dkar rdo rje gsang mchog chen po ste //
NK029(ha)003:1427: rtogs bral mnyam nyid ye shes rdo rje yis //
NK029(ha)003:1428: rtogs pa'i bgegs rnams rab tu zhi mdzad pa //
NK029(ha)003:1429: bkra shis des kyang bgegs rnams rab tu zhi bar shog /
NK029(ha)003:1430: yungs dkar rdo rjes bgegs mchog 'dul //
NK029(ha)003:1431: bgegs rnams 'joms pa'i mthu stobs ldan //
NK029(ha)003:1432: dgra bgegs kun las rgyal ba'i byin rlabs bkra shis le'u ste don brgyad pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:1433: gnyis pa zho phor gyi dbang ni /
NK029(ha)003:1434: sngon bcom ldan 'das la khyim bdag bzang skyong gis zho phul bas /
NK029(ha)003:1435: gzi mdangs dang ldan pa'i rdzas 'di /
NK029(ha)003:1437: slob ma khyod la sbyin pas /
NK029(ha)003:1438: khyod kyis ting nge 'dzin gyi bcud dang bsod nams
NK029(ha)003:1439: gzi mdangs dang ldan pa'i don gyi bkra shis par
NK029(ha)003:1440: gyur cig / zho ni kun gyi snying por gyur pa ste //
NK029(ha)003:1441: snying po rnam dag byang chub sems rtogs ste //
NK029(ha)003:1442: yon tan kun gyi snying por gyur pa yis //
NK029(ha)003:1443: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir zhi bar shog /
NK029(ha)003:1444: bkra shis byin ldan rdzas mchog zho mchog 'dis //'dod don mchog ldan 'dod 'jo ba'i zho //
NK029(ha)003:1445: nyon mongs 'phongs pa 'grangs zhing tshims byed pa /
NK029(ha)003:1446: gzi mdags ldan pa dbang gis bkra shis le'u don dgu pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:1447: gsum pa rtsa dur ba'i dbang ni /
NK029(ha)003:1448: sngon bcom ldan 'das la bram ze kun d+ha lis r+ts+wa dur ba phul ste /
NK029(ha)003:1449: dur ba ji ltar chung ngu las yal ga dang lo 'dab mang po 'phel ba bzhin du /
NK029(ha)003:1450: rgyu dge ba'i rtsa ba chung ngu las 'bras bu
NK029(ha)003:1451: bsod nams mang po 'phel ba'i byin gyis brlabs pa'i
NK029(ha)003:1452: rdzas 'di slob ma la byin pas /
NK029(ha)003:1453: chos rgyu 'bras la ma rmoongs shing dge ba'i rtsa
NK029(ha)003:1454: ba chung ngu la rten nas bsod nams 'bras bu
NK029(ha)003:1455: phun sum 'phel ba'i don gyis bkra shis par gyur
NK029(ha)003:1456: cig / dur bas tshe ni 'phel bar byed pa ste /
NK029(ha)003:1457: rdo rje tshe ni rab bsgrub pas //
NK029(ha)003:1458: skye shi'i sdug bsngal rgyun bcad de //
NK029(ha)003:1459: dur bas bkra shis des ni tshe brtan shog /
NK029(ha)003:1460: dur ba'i r+ts+wa mchog bsod nams mang pos 'phel //
NK029(ha)003:1461: bkra shis lo 'dab me tog 'bras bu rgyas //
NK029(ha)003:1462: yid la ci bsam 'dod pa'i bkra shis pa //'dod 'byung bkra shis le'u brgyad bcu pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:1464: sngon bcom ldan 'das la sa'i lha mos 'tshal li khri phul bas /
NK029(ha)003:1465: ji ltar li khri dmar po chags pa zhen pa'i ngo bo na gnas pa de bzhin du /
NK029(ha)003:1466: thugs rje chen pos sems can thams cad mi btang bar byin gyis brlabs pa'i rdzas 'di /
NK029(ha)003:1467: ngas slob ma khyod la byin pas khyod kyis sems
NK029(ha)003:1468: can thams cad kyi don byed cing 'khor ba'i chos
NK029(ha)003:1469: thams cad la spyod pa'i chos thams cad la sbyod
NK029(ha)003:1470: bzhin ma chags pa'i don gyis bkra shis par gyur
NK029(ha)003:1471: cig / li khri dmar ba dbang gi rang bzhin ste //
NK029(ha)003:1472: chos kun ma lus dbang du gyur pa ste //
NK029(ha)003:1473: chos kyi rgyal srid rab tu bstan gyur pa //
NK029(ha)003:1474: bkra shis des kyang rgyal srid bstan gyur cig /
NK029(ha)003:1475: kha dog dmar po nub phyogs dbang gi pad+ma'i rigs /
NK029(ha)003:1476: chags pa gnyis ldan bdag don gzhan don 'grub //
NK029(ha)003:1477: gsung gi bdag nyid don ston bkra shis rdzas //
NK029(ha)003:1478: tshe yis bkra shis le'u ste gya gcig pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:1479: lnga pa me long gi dbang /
NK029(ha)003:1480: sngon bcom ldan 'das kyis rnam par shes pa gnas
NK029(ha)003:1481: lan gsum du gar pa me long lta bu'i ye
NK029(ha)003:1482: shes bsnyes nas mngon par rdzogs pa'i rdzas 'di slob
NK029(ha)003:1484: khyod kyi bag chags gyi sgrib pa bag la nyal
NK029(ha)003:1485: cha phra mo yan chad rdo rje lta bu'i ting
NK029(ha)003:1486: nge 'dzin gyis bcom nas kun gzhi'i rnam par shes
NK029(ha)003:1488: me long ye shes mthong nas mngon par rdzogs par
NK029(ha)003:1489: sangs rgyas pa de'i don gyis bkra shis par gyur
NK029(ha)003:1490: cig / me long ye shes chen po'i gzugs brnyan ste //
NK029(ha)003:1491: ye shes rgyal mtsho'i bdag nyid mchog gyur nas //
NK029(ha)003:1492: rnam dag chos la thogs med longs spyod pas //
NK029(ha)003:1493: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir sgriib pa dag gyur cig /
NK029(ha)003:1494: me long gdong bstan bzhin gyi dri ma sel //
NK029(ha)003:1495: de bzhin nyon mongs shes bya'i sgrib pa sel //
NK029(ha)003:1496: gsal la rang bzhin med pa'i chos nyid la //
NK029(ha)003:1497: ye shes gsal ba'i bkra shis le'u ste gya gnyis pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:1499: sngon ri rab ri'i rtser rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la dung gis dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)003:1500: tshangs pa'i sgra sgrogs par gyur to //
NK029(ha)003:1501: de dang rjes su mthun par dung gi dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)003:1502: tshangs pa'i dbyangs lta bu sgrog pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)003:1503: chos dung rgyal bas bus nas ni //'jig rten sems can skal ldan la //
NK029(ha)003:1504: rnam gsal sdig byang chos thob pa'i //
NK029(ha)003:1505: tshangs pa'i sgra skad sgrogs par shog /
NK029(ha)003:1506: skyob pa mgon po tshangs pa'i dbyangs //'phags pa'i gsung
NK029(ha)003:1507: mchog 'gro la sgrog /'jig rten gsum du rgyas pa
NK029(ha)003:1508: yis // gsung gi bkra shis le'u ste gya gsum pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:1509: bdun pa g+hi hang gi dbang ni /
NK029(ha)003:1510: sngon bcom ldan 'das la glang po che sa bsrungs gis sman g+hi hang phul ste /
NK029(ha)003:1511: bee d+aur+ya dang ldan pa'i sman mchog bdud bzhi las grol bar byin gyis brlabs pa'i rdzas 'di /
NK029(ha)003:1512: ngas slob ma la byin pas slob ma'i bdud bzhi
NK029(ha)003:1513: las thar zhing nad thams cad sel bar byed pa'i
NK029(ha)003:1514: mthu phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan pa'i don gyis
NK029(ha)003:1516: g+hi hang dug gsum 'joms pa'i sman yin ste //
NK029(ha)003:1517: sman mchog chos nyid rab tu rtogs 'gyur te //
NK029(ha)003:1518: nyon mongs zung ngu med par gyur pa yis //
NK029(ha)003:1519: bkra shis des kyang sdug bsngal med par shog /
NK029(ha)003:1520: yon tan ldan pas bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi sel //
NK029(ha)003:1521: sman mchog skye 'gro ma lus kun gyis gsos //
NK029(ha)003:1522: byin gyis rlobs pa'i bkra shis tshe yis gsos //
NK029(ha)003:1523: tshe ring nad med bkra shis le'u ste gya bzhi pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:1525: sngon bcom ldan 'das la shing bil ba phyag du
NK029(ha)003:1526: phul te ji ltar shing bil ba smin cing 'bras
NK029(ha)003:1527: bu sa'i ngo bor gnas pa bzhin du /
NK029(ha)003:1528: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das kyis sku dang ye shes
NK029(ha)003:1529: dang stobs dang mi 'jigs pa la sogs pa 'bras
NK029(ha)003:1530: bu'i chos thams cad yongs su rdzogs par byin gyis
NK029(ha)003:1533: khyod la stobs bcu mi 'jigs pa bzhi dang /
NK029(ha)003:1534: ma 'dres pa bco brgyad dang ldan par sku dang
NK029(ha)003:1535: ye shes dang mtshan dang dpe byad la sogs ste
NK029(ha)003:1536: / 'bras bu'i chos thams cad yongs su rdzogs par
NK029(ha)003:1537: sangs rgyas pa'i don gyi bkra shis par gyur cig
NK029(ha)003:1538: / / bil ba rgyu rkyen 'bras bur bcas pa'i
NK029(ha)003:1539: mchog /'jig rten 'jig rten 'das pa'i spyod pa kun
NK029(ha)003:1540: / / // byang chub snying po mchog tu gyur pa yis //
NK029(ha)003:1541: bkra shis des kyang 'jig rten 'grub par shog /
NK029(ha)003:1542: yal ga lo 'dab me tog g.yu lor 'khyiil //'bras bu yid 'ong 'byor pa'i longs spyod ldan //
NK029(ha)003:1543: kun gyi don dang mthun par spyod pa yis //
NK029(ha)003:1544: phun tshogs bkra shis le'u ste gya lnga pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:1545: dgu pa thugs dpal be'i dbang /
NK029(ha)003:1546: sngon bcom ldan 'das la byang chub kyi shing drung du /
NK029(ha)003:1547: bdud kyi brgal ba'i dus su /
NK029(ha)003:1548: bkra shis pa'i rtags brgyad dang ldan ste /
NK029(ha)003:1549: thugs dpal be'usa bkra shis pa de bzhin du slob
NK029(ha)003:1550: ma'i thugs dpal be'u ru bkra shis par gyur cig
NK029(ha)003:1551: / dpal be'u thugs kyi sa bon ste //'dren pa rnams kyi thugs lags pas //
NK029(ha)003:1552: bla med thar lam drangs pa'i phyir //
NK029(ha)003:1553: thugs kyi dpal be'u bkra shis shog /
NK029(ha)003:1554: gzhan gyis mi thub che ba'i rtags dang ldan //
NK029(ha)003:1555: sdo ba'i phyogs rnams kun las rgyal //
NK029(ha)003:1556: thugs kha nyid las gsal ba mngon par ston //'di
NK029(ha)003:1557: ni dpal be'u dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste gya
NK029(ha)003:1558: drug pa'o // ston la bdud kyi sdos pa'i tshe //
NK029(ha)003:1559: thugs kyi dpal be'u bkra shis 'gyur //
NK029(ha)003:1560: de ring khyod la byin byas pas //
NK029(ha)003:1561: thams cad mkhyen pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK029(ha)003:1562: thugs dpal be'u bkra shis pas //
NK029(ha)003:1563: thams cad mkhyen pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)003:1564: bcu pa phyag zhabs tsakra'i dbang ni /
NK029(ha)003:1565: sngon bcom ldan 'das la bdud kyis rgal ba'i dus su bkra shis pa'i rtags brgyad byung ste /
NK029(ha)003:1566: phyag dang zhabs kyi mthil 'khor los bkra shis pa /
NK029(ha)003:1567: de bzhin du ming 'di zhes bya ba la 'khor los dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)003:1568: phyag dang zhabs kyi mthil 'khor los bkra shis par
NK029(ha)003:1569: gyur cig /'khor los bkra shis phyag dang zhabs mthil
NK029(ha)003:1570: la // skyobs pa'i sangs rgyas 'dren pa lha'i lha //
NK029(ha)003:1571: nyon mongs sems can sman pa'i gsos //
NK029(ha)003:1572: phyag zhabs 'khor los bkra shis shog /
NK029(ha)003:1573: gzhan gyi mi thub che ba'i rtags dang ldan //

NK029(ha)003:1837: nyes pa legs pa'i dgongs pa 'grub //
NK029(ha)003:1838: zhabs dub dbang gi bkra shis le'u brgya gsum pa'o /
NK029(ha)003:1839: bzhi pa phyag gdub kyi dbang ni /
NK029(ha)003:1840: sngon ri rab ri'i rtser dpal rnam par snang mdzad
NK029(ha)003:1841: kyis 'khor rnams la phyag gdub kyi dbang bskur bas
NK029(ha)003:1842: / tshul 'khrims rnam par dag pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK029(ha)003:1843: de dang rjes su mthun par phyag gdub kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)003:1844: tshul khrims rnam par dag pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)003:1845: sil snyan mdzes pa'i brgyan lags pas //
NK029(ha)003:1846: yid 'ong snyan pa'i phyag gdub 'di //'bras bu thob pa'i dbang mchog ste /
NK029(ha)003:1847: 'gro ba yid 'ong dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK029(ha)003:1848: rin chen phyag gdub dam pa 'di //
NK029(ha)003:1849: legs par mdzes pa'i yon tan gyis /
NK029(ha)003:1850: nges par legs pa'i dgongs pa 'grub //
NK029(ha)003:1851: phyag gdub dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste brgya bzhi pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:1852: lnga pa do shal gyi dbang ni /
NK029(ha)003:1853: sngon ri rab ri'i rtser dpal kun rig rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la //
NK029(ha)003:1854: rin po che do shal gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)003:1855: che ba'i yon tan rgyal ba'i dbang thob par gyur to //
NK029(ha)003:1856: de dang rjes su mthun par rin po che'i do shal gyis dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)003:1857: legs pa'i yon tan rdzogs shing mthar phyin pas //
NK029(ha)003:1858: che ba'i yon tan rgyas pa'i dbang dam pa thob par cig /
NK029(ha)003:1859: rin chen 'phreng pas 'gro ba'i re 'dod bskongs /
NK029(ha)003:1860: phreng ba do shal 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa /
NK029(ha)003:1861: yon tan tshangs pa'i brgyan mchog dam pa 'di /
NK029(ha)003:1862: 'bras bu yid bzhin bkra shis thob par shog /
NK029(ha)003:1863: rin chen 'phreng ba'i do shal dam pa 'di //
NK029(ha)003:1864: sku yi brgyan mchog yon tan sku la brgyan //'phreng ma chad cing rgyun ma chad mdzad pa //
NK029(ha)003:1865: rin chen 'phreng dbang bkra shis le'u ste brgya lnga pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:1866: drug pa dar gyi cod pan gyi dbang ni /
NK029(ha)003:1867: sngon ri rab ri'i rtser rnam par snang mdzad kyi
NK029(ha)003:1868: 'khor rnams la dar gyi cod pan gyis dbang bskur
NK029(ha)003:1869: bas // rdul gyis bag chags dang bral bar gyur to //
NK029(ha)003:1870: de dang rjes su mthun par dar gyi cod pan gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)003:1871: sbyor bas khams gsum na gnas na yang /
NK029(ha)003:1872: rdul gyi bag chags dang bral bar gyur to //
NK029(ha)003:1873: bkra shis rtags ldan dar gyi cod pan 'di //
NK029(ha)003:1874: dbang gi rang bzhin dmar po 'bar ba te //
NK029(ha)003:1875: dbang bskur spyi bor rtags pa'i yon tan gyis //
NK029(ha)003:1876: dbang gi bkra shis dam pa thob par shog /
NK029(ha)003:1877: chos nyid dar dang 'dra bar mtshungs pa yis //
NK029(ha)003:1878: don dam nyid du rtogs pa mngon phyung zhing //'di nyid legs pa'i chos nyid don rtogs pa //
NK029(ha)003:1879: byin rlabs dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste brgya drug pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:1880: bcu pa ming gi dbang la gnyis las /
NK029(ha)003:1881: dang po rgyu'i ming gi dbang la /
NK029(ha)003:1882: sngon ri rab ri'i rtser dpal rnam par snang mdzad
NK029(ha)003:1883: kyis 'khor rnams la rdo rje ming gi dbang bskur
NK029(ha)003:1884: bas / rigs nges pa'i sras su gyur nas rdo rje 'chang gi gral thob par gyur to //
NK029(ha)003:1885: de dang rjes su mthun par rdo rje ming gi dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)003:1886: mi 'gyur ba'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)003:1887: rdo rje ming mchog mkhas pa dpe la drangs //
NK029(ha)003:1888: thugs las gsung du byung nas rtags pa 'di //
NK029(ha)003:1889: dag cing tshul du khyed la bskur ba yis //
NK029(ha)003:1890: thams cad ston pa'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK029(ha)003:1891: ston pa thugs rjes nges pa'i ming btags pas //
NK029(ha)003:1892: thugs kyi ngang nas nges pa'i sras su mdzad //
NK029(ha)003:1893: rdo rje mchog gi gral thob ming gi dbang //
NK029(ha)003:1894: rdo rje ming dbang bkra shis le'u brgya bdun pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:1895: gnyis pa 'bras bu'i ming gi dbang /
NK029(ha)003:1896: sngon ri rab ri'i rtser rgyal bu don thams cad
NK029(ha)003:1897: grub pa la rigs bzhi'i sangs rgyas kyi mngon par
NK029(ha)003:1898: shes pa lngas dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)003:1900: rin po che'i khang bu 'bar bar rnam par snang
NK029(ha)003:1901: mdzad mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas par gyur to
NK029(ha)003:1902: // de dang rjes su mthun par mngon par byang chub pa lngas dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)003:1903: 'bras bu ri rab ri'i rtser mngon par sangs rgyas par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)003:1904: mngon shes lnga ldan 'bras bu sa bcu 'das /
NK029(ha)003:1905: yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen sa la gnas /
NK029(ha)003:1906: 'bras bu dam pa sangs rgyas te /
NK029(ha)003:1907: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i dbang mchog dam pa thob par shog /
NK029(ha)003:1908: dbang mchog thams cad yongs su rdzogs pa yi //'bras bu thams cad ma lus thob pa ste //
NK029(ha)003:1909: rdo rje rgyal po'i dbang mchog der rdzogs pas //'di
NK029(ha)003:1910: ni phyi dbang rdzogs pa'i bkra shis le'u ste brgya
NK029(ha)003:1911: rtsa brgyad pa'o // ab+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK029(ha)003:1912: dbang don rgyas pa'i dbye ba ltar sbyar ba yin no //
NK029(ha)003:1913: spyir phyi dbang la brgya rtsa brgyad yod do /
NK029(ha)003:1914: ka smad nyan rang gi dbang ma rtogs so /
NK029(ha)003:1916: gnyis pa nus pa'i dbang la lnga ste /
NK029(ha)003:1921: rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams kyi dbang ngo /
NK029(ha)003:1922: dbang de lnga'i cho ga yang gong dang mthun no //
NK029(ha)003:1923: gsum pa gsang ba zab mo'i dbang la gsum ste /
NK029(ha)003:1925: shes rab ye shes kyi dbang dang /
NK029(ha)003:1926: dbyer med bde ba chen po'i dbang ngo //
NK029(ha)003:1927: dbang de gsum gyi cho ga'i dod la /
NK029(ha)003:1929: lha lam khyer lha tshogs sum cu rtsa bdun //
NK029(ha)003:1930: snying po lam khyer bud+d+ha bee ro tsa na //
NK029(ha)003:1934: a mo g+ha sid d+hi a /
NK029(ha)003:1936: theg pa lam khyer yo ga'i theg pa /
NK029(ha)003:1937: dbang lam khyer yo ga'i dbang mchog drug cu rtsa gnyis so //
NK029(ha)003:1938: de la dbang chags pa'i rten du 'debs gcig byas na /
NK029(ha)003:1939: rang gi snying gi dkyil na dngas ma chen po lnga gnas pa ni /
NK029(ha)003:1940: rang bzhin gyi rigs lnga dang ye shes lnga'i ngo bor gdod ma nas gnas pa yin te /
NK029(ha)003:1941: de la rang gi spyi bor thig le dkar po ril ma tsam gcig bsam /
NK029(ha)003:1943: nam mkha'i dkyil nas thil pa shar /
NK029(ha)003:1945: thig le dkar po de yas mas babs pas /
NK029(ha)003:1946: snying gi dkyil du dngas ma lnga'i rigs lngar gnas pa dang gnyis su med par 'dres pa bsam /
NK029(ha)003:1947: de ni don dam mtshan ma med pa'i ngo bo nyid do //
NK029(ha)003:1948: rigs lngar gnas shing rigs lnga rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor gyi lhar snang ba ni /
NK029(ha)003:1949: kun rdzob ye shes snang ba ste //
NK029(ha)003:1950: de dag gnyis su med pa'i ngang las /
NK029(ha)003:1951: blo rang bzhin gyi gnas pa ni /
NK029(ha)003:1952: dbang chags pa'i rten yin gsung nga //
NK029(ha)003:1953: de la yo ga'i gags sbyar na /
NK029(ha)003:1954: gang du bskur ba'i gnas ni /
NK029(ha)003:1955: lha bya skad snyan ljon shing gi tshal rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor du /
NK029(ha)003:1956: gang gis bskur ba'i ston pa ni /
NK029(ha)003:1957: slob dpon chen po kun ma tis bskur /
NK029(ha)003:1958: gang la bskur ba'i yul ni /
NK029(ha)003:1959: rdo rje khyung grags rtsal la sogs pa'o //
NK029(ha)003:1961: yo ga bkra shis drug cu rtsa bzhi'i dbang bskur ste /
NK029(ha)003:1962: rgyu mtshan ni bcom ldan 'das dpal rnam par snang mdzad kyis /
NK029(ha)003:1963: bcom ldan 'das che ba'i yon tan smos pa'i phyir ro //
NK029(ha)003:1964: dgos pa ni gang gis thob pa'i bkra shis par bya ba'i phyir dgos pa yod do //
NK029(ha)003:1969: tshogs dang dga' ston rgya chen bya /
NK029(ha)003:1974: bstod pa ci rigs pa bya /
NK029(ha)003:1976: de ltar bdag nyid chen po khyed rnams la /
NK029(ha)003:1977: bsnyen cing sgrub pa dang ci 'byor ba'i /
NK029(ha)003:1978: yo byad rnams kyi mchod pa la ci 'byor ba'i mchod pa grangs ji snyed pa phul bas /
NK029(ha)003:1979: bdag dang mtha' yas pa'i sems can thams cad /
NK029(ha)003:1982: bla na med pa'i byang chub chen po thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)003:1984: gang yang bdag brtsod pa'i dus su snyigs ma'i sems can du gyur nas /
NK029(ha)003:1985: gzhung bzhin du yo byad ma tshogs pa dang /
NK029(ha)003:1987: de dag thams cad bdag nyid chen po 'khor dang
NK029(ha)003:1988: bcas pa khyed rnams kyis bzod pa chen po mdzad
NK029(ha)003:1989: du gsol / gzhan yang bdag cag las dang po pa'i sems can du gyur bas /
NK029(ha)003:1990: ting 'dzin la dbang ma thob te /
NK029(ha)003:1991: cho ga'i yan lag la bying ba dang /
NK029(ha)003:1993: 'dod chags la sogs pa nyon mongs pa'i dbang gis /
NK029(ha)003:1997: cho ga nyams pa de dag thams cad bdag nyid
NK029(ha)003:1998: chen po 'khor dang bcas pa khyed rnams kyis bzod
NK029(ha)003:2000: gang yang bdag blo gti mug pas //
NK029(ha)003:2001: legs byas 'di la nyes bya gang //
NK029(ha)003:2002: gang phyir lus can skyabs gyur pas //
NK029(ha)003:2003: de ni mgon pos bzod par gsol //
NK029(ha)003:2004: rtsol ba'i nus phan ma mching shing //
NK029(ha)003:2005: ma rnyed pa dang ma tshang ba dang //'dir ni bya ba gang 'gyis pa //
NK029(ha)003:2006: de dag thams cad bzod par gsol /
NK029(ha)003:2008: khyed kyis sems can don kun mdzad //
NK029(ha)003:2009: rjes su mthun pa'i dngos grub stsol //
NK029(ha)003:2010: rtag tu gshegs pa ma lags kyang //
NK029(ha)003:2011: sems can don la dgongs nas kyang //
NK029(ha)003:2012: slar yang 'byon par mdzad du gsol //
NK029(ha)003:2013: badz+ra muh bkra shis brjod pa ni /
NK029(ha)003:2014: ston mchog dam pa lha mi mchod 'os pa'i //
NK029(ha)003:2015: ces sogs kyi bkra shis brjod /
NK029(ha)003:2017: de ni yo ga'i dbang gi them skas rdzogs so //
